Malva
=====

What is Malva?
--------------

Malva is a test suite for alternative JVMs. It tests core Java API classes such
as java.lang.Class and java.lang.Object that require implementation on the JVM
side.

Running the Test Suite
----------------------

To compile the test suite with 'javac' and run the tests with 'java' use:

  make check

All tests should pass.

If you want to use an alternative compiler or JVM pass the JAVAC and JAVA
options to make:

  make check JAVAC=ecj JAVA=cacao

